high_descs: Head to the end of the passage on the left and turn right to enter the room with the table.
Pick up the pink soap from the table.
Turn left and walk out the room and take a right to face the table lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn the table lamp on with soap in hand.

high_descs: Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the desk on your right.
Pick up soap bar from the desk.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a soap bar by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step forward before heading right into a hallway, enter the last room on the right and walk all the way to a table
Pick up a remote from the table.
Leave the room via the same entrance and move right to a lamp.
Use the remote to switch on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp with the remote

high_descs: Head toward the desk then turn right to reach the lamp.
Turn right to reach the table and pick the soapbar from the table.
Turn left go straight near to the floorlamp.
anns.task_desc: See the SoapBar by the light of a tall FloorLamp.
